{"tid":1667220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲黑警OT咁多黎做咩，反正佢地退休之後既早死率都較高","createTime":"2019-10-21T10:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T12:44:49.000Z","uid":214534,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"762cbe557481198fff4a59237c1e99abcbac6b69","tid":1667220,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20100629/14185175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100629%2F14185175&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNkoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=01c952dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100629%2F14185175&h=83a86acc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20100629/14185175</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>工時長積勞成疾有長俸冇命享懲教員兩成退休後五年過世 <span style=\"color: red;\">身體必有病</span>| 蘋果日報| 要聞港聞| 20100629</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">紀律部隊內一直流傳，部門員工積勞成疾，退休後容易早死，但政府從未公佈有關數據。據了解，懲教署員方最近做了非正式統計得出「震撼結果」</span></span>：粗略估計逾兩成員工，在退休後五年內逝世，終年只有約60歲，較香港男性平均壽命79.5歲，明顯命短一截，有終生長俸也「冇命享」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係喎係喎人工普遍比私人市場非專科高啵 <br />\n我先唔要呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n退休後又特別早死 就算唔死都多病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw祝願紀律部隊既黃絲，一生平平安安，富貴逼人來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4198ce8b7dd9e54aa98fb4d65f75358431e7fa3f","tid":1667220,"uid":258696,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"幫手用魔法減低佢地平均壽命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed09ab51c9a9e5fe2d2238e21a63d505a9d8edc8","tid":1667220,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"想黑警即刻退休"},{"pid":"533a87a745c1e9cd783bd90433927c3fd996c243","tid":1667220,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f0b25c48951fd5c266077dbf7917c0ae7284aa","tid":1667220,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏嘅同我入嚟<br />\n快啲把握最好時機</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6766c961fbbafa1a91a1ccf95c8c95ffd5590de8","tid":1667220,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c72a4374c1ea5a75289976d2817bcd66d2856ac","tid":1667220,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"63282a9189edb2596114a84612f9d7742c9ae426","tid":1667220,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037f9498f2158fe9eb6651de1b31c35240506d50","tid":1667220,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"留俾佢地老婆勾佬"},{"pid":"44b6ed32f1cddee0253967455c15e8e0b6775911","tid":1667220,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37c702f29126bdb04cd042daa7e77b0bbae19915","tid":1667220,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"94919a2bdb5fc4d6e3d50d9f864632230c74d65a","tid":1667220,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"037f9498f2158fe9eb6651de1b31c35240506d50","tid":1667220,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"留俾佢地老婆勾佬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0300e3872a129e2c